@startuml AD_LT_04_Log_Sample_Chain_of_Custody

title AD_LT_04 — Log Sample Chain-of-Custody Event

|Lab Technician|
|System|

|Lab Technician|

note
  Prerequisites:
  - AD_LT_00 User Authenticated
  - Sample record exists in system
end note

start

:Navigate to Sample Tracking module;
:Scan barcode or enter sample ID;

|System|

if (Sample ID found?) then (no)
  :Return error message;
  |Lab Technician|
  :Verify sample ID\nor register sample first;
  |System|
else (yes)
  :Retrieve and display\ncurrent custody history;
endif

|Lab Technician|

:Select event type;

if (Event type?) then (Received)
  :Confirm receipt;

else (Processed)
  :Confirm processing;

else (Stored)
  :Confirm storage location;

else (Transferred)
  :Enter recipient name\nand role / department;

  |System|

  if (Recipient details provided?) then (no)
    :Block submission;\nRecipient required;
    |Lab Technician|
    :Enter recipient details;
    |System|
  else (yes)
  endif

else (Discarded)
  |Lab Technician|
  :Select disposal reason code\nfrom controlled list;
  :Enter disposal method;

  |System|

  if (Reason code provided?) then (no)
    :Block submission;\nReason code required;
    |Lab Technician|
    :Select reason code;
    |System|
  else (yes)
  endif

  :Require disposal confirmation;
  |Lab Technician|
  :Confirm disposal;
  |System|
endif

|System|

:Record custody event:\n- Event type\n- Timestamp\n- Technician ID\n- Additional notes;

:Display updated\nchain-of-custody log;

|Lab Technician|

:View updated custody log;

stop

@enduml
